    <briefdescription>
<para>Simple class for passing around pairs of small unsigned integers. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Use this for integer dimensions and points with limited range such as image sizes and pixel coordinates where a pair of floating point numbers is inefficient and illogical (i.e. the data is inherently integer). One of these can be passed in a single 32 bit integer register on common architectures. @SINCE_1_0.0 </para>
    </detaileddescription>
